(46, 'ISPARTA ISO Zirvesi (22-23 ARALIK 2018)', '<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">ISPARTA!</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Kariyerine ve Geleceğine Y&ouml;n Ver!</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Eğitim Zirvelerine &ouml;nc&uuml;l&uuml;k eden Sinerji Eğitim &amp; Organizasyon, Organizekşın işbirliğiyle geleceğinize y&ouml;n verecek yepyeni bir ISO EĞİTİM ZİRVESİ d&uuml;zenliyor. &Uuml;stelik Akreditite Kuruluştan onaylı 10 ULUSLARARASI SERTİFİKALI!</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">(5 T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e - 5 İngilizce)</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">TARİH: 22-23 Aralık 2018</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">SAAT: 10.00-17.00</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">YER: English Time Isparta</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">EĞİTİM ve SERTİFİKALAR: .</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">-ISO 9001 :2015 Kalite Y&ouml;netim Sistemi Eğitimi .</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">-İ&ccedil; Denet&ccedil;ili